{"data":[{"id":"102_1753853819.957","type":"feed","offset":102,"verb":"TOPIC_ACKNOWLEDGED_ANSWER","created_time":1753853819,"updated_time":1753853819,"target":{"id":"1923316886394869255","type":"answer","url":"https://api.zhihu.com/answers/1923316886394869255","author":{"id":"cd2b08c55994913a681f7ec3d1a79b5c","url":"https://api.zhihu.com/people/cd2b08c55994913a681f7ec3d1a79b5c","user_type":"people","url_token":"69-37-51-64","name":"新烁","headline":"","avatar_url":"https://pic1.zhimg.com/50/v2-96a44049c834c06e2c391c20b807048c_l.jpg?source=b6762063","is_org":false,"gender":0,"followers_count":355,"is_following":false,"is_followed":false},"created_time":1751334479,"updated_time":1751334498,"voteup_count":1050,"thanks_count":42,"comment_count":144,"is_copyable":true,"question":{"id":"563683181","type":"question","url":"https://api.zhihu.com/questions/563683181","author":{"id":"f59d748a1542a31e28cd5e61953508c4","url":"https://api.zhihu.com/people/f59d748a1542a31e28cd5e61953508c4","user_type":"people","url_token":"zhi-xing-1hao","name":"执行1号","headline":"","avatar_url":"https://pic1.zhimg.com/50/v2-5f39998435bf223d269d28cb37a55474_l.jpg?source=b6762063","is_org":false,"gender":-1,"followers_count":4,"is_following":false,"is_followed":false},"title":"孙宇晨为什么能这么成功？","created":1667201864,"answer_count":0,"follower_count":0,"comment_count":4,"bound_topic_ids":[99,1740,119293,169813,213207],"is_following":false,"excerpt":"","relationship":{"is_author":false},"detail":"","question_type":"normal"},"excerpt":"我只说两个点。 一，对经济趋势的判断 孙在他2016年的音频节目中就已经明确的说到： 东大的未来经济环境将进入一个长期的滞涨，甚至是长期的低增长，负增长。其中最悲催的将会是90后，因为90后将是刚步入壮年就要目睹东大经济下滑的一代人。 二，站在宏观国际角度看，他认为什么样的价值观（意识形态）最终会取胜？ 1，建立在自由意志主义和利己主义上 2，敢于承认和保护私有产权 3，宣传个人奋斗，创造科技进步的互联网价值观 …","excerpt_new":"我只说两个点。 一，对经济趋势的判断 孙在他2016年的音频节目中就已经明确的说到： 东大的未来经济环境将进入一个长期的滞涨，甚至是长期的低增长，负增长。其中最悲催的将会是90后，因为90后将是刚步入壮年就要目睹东大经济下滑的一代人。 二，站在宏观国际角度看，他认为什么样的价值观（意识形态）最终会取胜？ 1，建立在自由意志主义和利己主义上 2，敢于承认和保护私有产权 3，宣传个人奋斗，创造科技进步的互联网价值观 …","preview_type":"default","preview_text":"","reshipment_settings":"allowed","content":"\u003cp data-pid=\"pI4IAzn4\"\u003e我只说两个点。\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp class=\"ztext-empty-paragraph\"\u003e\u003cbr/\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp data-pid=\"jhjOENsv\"\u003e一，对经济趋势的判断\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp data-pid=\"pbAO9K54\"\u003e孙在他2016年的音频节目中就已经明确的说到：\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp data-pid=\"Wx2CPejx\"\u003e\u003cb\u003e东大的未来经济环境将进入一个长期的滞涨，甚至是长期的低增长，负增长。\u003c/b\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp data-pid=\"l0x6TMQN\"\u003e其中最悲催的将会是90后，因为90后将是刚步入壮年就要目睹东大经济下滑的一代人。\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp class=\"ztext-empty-paragraph\"\u003e\u003cbr/\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp data-pid=\"sD8mcIps\"\u003e二，站在宏观国际角度看，他认为什么样的价值观（意识形态）最终会取胜？\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp data-pid=\"NnNWVGk6\"\u003e1，建立在自由意志主义和利己主义上\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp data-pid=\"7Y7PVix7\"\u003e2，敢于承认和保护私有产权\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp data-pid=\"DF5Y1FIw\"\u003e\u003cb\u003e3，宣传个人奋斗，创造科技进步的互联网价值观\u003c/b\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp class=\"ztext-empty-paragraph\"\u003e\u003cbr/\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp data-pid=\"8PdrYyts\"\u003e目前来看，基本上都是正确的。\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp data-pid=\"0Hi4GgIl\"\u003e如果你能有他当时的判断能力，并且敢于下注，现在的资产不会低于8位数。\u003c/p\u003e","relationship":{"is_thanked":false,"is_nothelp":false,"voting":0},"is_labeled":false,"visited_count":75072,"favorite_count":612,"answer_type":"normal","is_navigator":false,"navigator_vote":false,"vote_next_step":"vote"},"brief":"{\"source\": \"TS\", \"type\": \"answer\", \"id\": 1923316886394869255}","attached_info":"","action_card":false},{"id":"103_1753853819.16","type":"feed","offset":103,"verb":"TOPIC_ACKNOWLEDGED_ANSWER","created_time":1753853819,"updated_time":1753853819,"target":{"id":"129570389974","type":"answer","url":"https://api.zhihu.com/answers/129570389974","author":{"id":"6f5b9e4189a7770bcae981d24ae6f76c","url":"https://api.zhihu.com/people/6f5b9e4189a7770bcae981d24ae6f76c","user_type":"people","url_token":"yu-wen-yue-74","name":"宇文玥","headline":"与来自世界的懂商业的人仕勾通新的异业合作，就是一件快乐的事","avatar_url":"https://picx.zhimg.com/50/v2-d390ad333bf14d4a0521816abe49be5a_l.jpg?source=